measurements.description:
One attractive flower and one bud on two 36-cm inflorescences;



 dorsal sepal white, caudae 4.5cm, orange tip; lateral sepals white blushed raspberry pink veined darker, dark pink-red linear markings proximally,
straight caudae 3.5cm, orange tips; 
 petals minute, white; lip minute, white tipped gold;

 column and anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte; caudae length included in sepal length measurement.
